{"tid":1287555,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英議員公開下令放催號彈英籍警司名字　警察評議會職方協會去信促道歉","createTime":"2019-07-05T09:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T11:20:48.000Z","uid":186431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"55afeb7c2a4cad2d155b0b135efa21fc9decdd55","tid":1287555,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3xh23E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3xh23E.jpg&h=53570afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國工黨國會議員古德曼（Helen Goodman）早前在下議院發言時，促請英國政府跟進，包括香港警司薛鎮廷（Justin Shave）在內的三名英籍警官，於6月12日處理香港示威時下令施放催號彈及開槍，涉以「殘酷」手段對待示威者一事。香港警察評議會職方協會就此去信古德曼，要求對方向薛鎮廷及香港警隊道歉。  協會批評古德曼公開薛鎮廷之名字，變相鼓鼓勵「起底」，而這三名英籍警官正受到極端網絡攻擊，其家屬亦遭受人身威脅。  協會指警方在6月12日清場時，已經使用最低武力，目的是恢復公共秩序及保護自己。協會指古德曼對港情況一無所知，又或是故意對真相視而不見，認為她欠了對薛鎮廷及香港警隊一個道歉。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-05-2019/54125?fbclid=IwAR0X1D6BiZ7MGnUawZp_Y6o17XS7mhrshk2cmpRVZiXZwYU8EsODnVGXAbY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-05-2019%2F54125%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0X1D6BiZ7MGnUawZp_Y6o17XS7mhrshk2cmpRVZiXZwYU8EsODnVGXAbY&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BD%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=7a404bba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-05-2019/54125?fbclid=IwAR0X1D6BiZ7MGnUawZp_Y6o17XS7mhrshk2cmpRVZiXZwYU8EsODnVGXAbY</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />薛鎮廷（Justin Shave）"},{"pid":"44dec842c61efaec54e79fbee14b9759d5d91109","tid":1287555,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:18:23.000Z","msg":"On差佬"},{"pid":"faf628a6eda655c5ba1daa2c6c08a8dd697786f4","tid":1287555,"uid":65530,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:19:55.00